<section class="section">
  <div class="container" style="max-width:800px;">
    <div class="eyebrow">Company</div>
    <h1>About Rofo</h1>

    <p class="lead">
      Rofo was founded in 2007 with a simple goal: make it easier for businesses to find the right commercial space.
    </p>

    <p>
      We started in San Francisco, working closely with small businesses navigating the complexities of office, retail, and industrial real estate. Over time, we expanded to markets across the United States, helping companies make more informed location decisions.
    </p>

    <p>
      Along the way, Rofo has consistently explored new ways to improve the search experience:
    </p>

    <ul style="margin:16px 0; padding-left:18px; line-height:1.7;">
      <li>Finalist for a Webby Award</li>
      <li>Built one of the first commercial real estate apps using augmented reality</li>
      <li>Selected as one of a small group of companies to build an app for LinkedIn</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      Most importantly, we’ve helped <strong>over 100,000 businesses</strong> connect with commercial real estate opportunities.
    </p>

    <p>
      Today, we’re continuing that mission by leveraging modern data and AI to make market discovery faster, clearer, and more useful for business owners.
    </p>

    <div class="panel" style="margin-top:40px;">
      <div class="kicker">Contact</div>
      <h3>Get in touch</h3>
      <p class="muted" style="margin-bottom:16px;">
        Have a question or looking for space? We’re here to help.
      </p>

      <div class="city-card">
  <div class="eyebrow">Contact</div>
  <h2>Tell us what you're looking for</h2>
  <p>We’ll follow up with a few relevant options.</p>

  <form
    action="https://formspree.io/f/xreoadbr"
    method="POST"
  >
    <input type="hidden" name="source" value="rofo-contact">
    <input type="hidden" name="page_type" value="contact">
    <input type="hidden" name="page_url" value="{{ page.url }}">

    <div class="form-stack">
      <div class="field">
        <label>Name</label>
        <input name="name" type="text" placeholder="Your name" required>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="form-stack">
      <div class="field">
        <label>Email</label>
        <input name="email" type="email" placeholder="you@example.com" required>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="form-stack">
      <div class="field">
        <label>Space needed <span class="optional">(optional)</span></label>
        <select name="space_needed">
          <option value="">Select one</option>
          <option>Under 1,000 sqft</option>
          <option>1,000–2,500 sqft</option>
          <option>2,500–5,000 sqft</option>
          <option>5,000–10,000 sqft</option>
          <option>10,000+ sqft</option>
        </select>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="form-stack">
      <div class="field">
        <label>Timeline <span class="optional">(optional)</span></label>
        <select name="timeline">
          <option value="">Select one</option>
          <option>ASAP</option>
          <option>Within 3 months</option>
          <option>Within 6 months</option>
          <option>6+ months</option>
          <option>Just exploring</option>
        </select>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="form-stack">
      <div class="field">
        <label>Anything else? <span class="optional">(optional)</span></label>
        <textarea name="notes"></textarea>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="btn-row">
      <button class="btn-primary" type="submit">Show Me Options</button>
    </div>

    <p class="form-note">
      No spam. Just helpful options to get you started.
    </p>
  </form>
</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
